Represents binary data
Annotation:

``binary``

Literal Syntax:

``0x[ffffffff]``
 - hex-based binary representation
``0o[1234567]``
 - octal-based binary representation
``0b[10101010101]``
 - binary-based binary representation
Casts:

[link: /commands/docs/into_binary.md] ``into binary``
See also:

[link: /book/types_of_data.md#binary-data] Types of data - Binary
